{"tid":2191513,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原來塞爾維亞今次簽嘅經濟協議，係包括咗不可使用「不受信任的供應商」","createTime":"2020-09-06T13:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T14:56:18.000Z","uid":290118,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"bacf0909ef3d8d926f66718a75edcc0dfb5e0991","tid":2191513,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpYKUe2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpYKUe2.jpg&h=f6355f49&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n年初肺炎大家笑過佢奶共<br />\n<br />\n但原來今次美帝斡旋，仲有一個重大意義，雙方今次簽署的經濟合約，都係認同唔再使用美國的「不可信任供應商」今次真係成為最大贏家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港媒體又淡化左成件事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/3007814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F3007814&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4m7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=8d2d0996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/3007814</a><br />\n以色列意外的外交豐收<br />\n其他外交事務方面，包含雙方同意遵循美國利益，將伊斯蘭組織真主黨（Hezbollah）認定為「恐怖組織」，並且同意禁止使用「不受信任的供應商所提供的通信網絡5G設備」，這條文大概是劍指中國。出乎外界意料的是，塞爾維亞宣布跟隨美國的腳步，準備於明年7月將其駐特拉維夫大使館遷移至耶路撒冷，而穆斯林國家科索沃也同意與以色列建立外交關係。"},{"pid":"d6e6b4299026024d8dd1f8233ae20d7efe804ab4","tid":2191513,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"倒戈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b26faf1aab23084a56efe09a037ca0c6e5505d4","tid":2191513,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"華為又贏"},{"pid":"50bfdcc2cf3dfaf105c00e2f2ddadbd5c86d3a92","tid":2191513,"uid":39855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bacf0909ef3d8d926f66718a75edcc0dfb5e0991","tid":2191513,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202